<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Contact Us - Smart Exchange</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #f0f4f8;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        .contact-us {
            padding: 80px 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 3em;
            text-align: center;
            color: #1a73e8;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-in;
        }

        .intro {
            font-size: 1.3em;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto 60px;
            color: #555;
            animation: slideUp 1s ease-out;
        }

        .content {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 80px;
        }

        .content-box {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 300px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, #e8f0fe 100%);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        .content-box:hover {
            transform: scale(1.03);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }

        .content-box h2 {
            font-size: 2em;
            color: #1a73e8;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .content-box h2::after {
            content: '';
            width: 50px;
            height: 3px;
            background: #34c759;
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -10px;
            left: 0;
        }

        .content-box p {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 15px; /* Adjusted for multiple lines */
        }

        .content-box a {
            color: #1a73e8;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .content-box a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        /* Animations */
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; }
            to { opacity: 1; }
        }

        @keyframes slideUp {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        /* Responsive Design */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .content {
                flex-direction: column;
                padding: 0;
            }
            h1 {
                font-size: 2.2em;
            }
            .intro {
                font-size: 1.1em;
            }
            .content-box {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            .content-box h2 {
                font-size: 1.6em;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .content-box {
                padding: 15px;
            }
            .content-box h2 {
                font-size: 1.5em;
            }
            .content-box p {
                font-size: 1em;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %> 
    <section class="contact-us">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Contact Smart Exchange</h1>
            <p class="intro">
                We're here to assist you with all your refurbished tech needs. Reach out to us for inquiries, support, or to learn more about Smart Exchange.
            </p>
            <div class="content">
                <div class="content-box">
                    <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
                    <p>Email: <a href="mailto:info@smartexchange.com">inf0@smartexchange.com</a></p>
                    <p>Phone: <a href="tel:+91 6304630478">+91 6304630478</a></p>
                    <p>We respond within 24 hours, Monday to Friday.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="content-box">
                    <h2>Support</h2>
                    <p>Need help with your device? Contact our support team:</p>
                    <p>Email: <a href="mailto:support@smartexchange.com">support@smartexchange.com</a></p>
                
                </div>
                <div class="content-box">
                    <h2>Visit Us</h2>
                    <p>Smart Exchange HQ</p>
                    <p>jublee hills, Hyderabad</p>
                    <p>Andhra Pradesh, CA 94405, India</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</body>
<footer><%- include('partials/footer') %> </footer>
</html>